data.description: This well-maintained home was fully renovated in 2021 including roof, siding, floor and carpets. Just blocks away from the water, this property represents a rare opportunity to purchase a completely move-in ready, 3 bed home in a fantastic neighborhood. The open floor plan, beautiful vinyl wood floors along with the modern kitchen with granite counter tops and stainless appliances are just a few of the features you will love about this home.  Large backyard has a new privacy fence and the floating deck, firepit, lighting and raised garden planters make this a perfect place to entertain or relax after a long day.  The property includes a detached storage shed with electricity and the long driveway runs the full length of the side of the property which can easily accommodate several cars, an RV or boat.  There is also a 240 volt outlet in the driveway ready for your electric car. The seller has a VA assumable loan at a 2.5% interest rate for qualified buyers.
